Terrorists are likely to try to carry out attacks in Mozambique. Attacks could be indiscriminate, including in places visited by foreigners.
The northern Cabo Delgado province has seen an increase in attacks in rural areas by groups with links to Islamic extremism. The FCO advise against all but essential travel to the districts of Palma, Mocimboa da Praia and Macomia in Cabo Delgado province.
